net.bytebuddy.instrumentation.method.matcher

Class MethodMatchers

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.bytebuddy.instrumentation.method.matcher.MethodMatchers

  • public final class MethodMatchers
extends Object
    A collection of common MethodMatcher implementations.

     

    This class is not meant to be instantiated but is usually imported statically in order to allow for improving the readability of code.
